ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer to the Commissioner of Nunavut (approximately 120 square metres)
PrecisOrder transfering to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of two surveyed parcels of land comprising the beds of bodies of water within two streams (approximately 120 square metres), within the municipal boundaries of the hamlet of Baker Lake.
